  • Method Details

    • composeFrame

      void composeFrame​(float position)
      This method is called with a value between 0 (start) and 1 (end). It should set up the animation state proportionally between these two conditions.
      Parameters:
      position - the interpolated position at which to compose the frame between the start and end key frames
